<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL45">
<l>vaḷaveḻun tavaḷa māṭa maturaimā nakaran taṉṉuṭ</l>
<l>kavaḷamāl yāṉai koṉṟa kaṇṇaṉai yaraṅka mālait</l>
<l>tuvaḷattoṇ ṭāya tolcīrt toṇṭara ṭippo ṭicol</l>
<l>liḷaiyapuṉ kavitai yēlu mempirāṟ kiṉiya vāṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Oh, how [this] poetry</l>
<l rend="indent">—even if it be immature [and] lowly,</l>
<l rend="indent">spoken by Toṇṭaraṭippoṭi of ancient excellence who [performed]</l>
<l rend="indent">tulasī[-offering] service</l>
<l rend="indent">on Māl from Raṅgam, Kṛṣṇa who killed the big elephant in musth</l>
<l rend="indent">inside the big city of Mathurā with white mansions of increased beauty—</l>
<l>is sweet to our Lord!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
